patthana19.12:1.1_0: Naparittaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca paritto dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana19.12:3.1_0: Naparittārammaṇaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca parittārammaṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana19.12:4.1_0: Hetuyā terasa, ārammaṇe terasa, adhipatiyā nava …pe… purejāte āsevane nava …pe… avigate terasa.
patthana19.12:5.1_0: Nahīnaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca majjhimo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana19.12:6.1_0: Hetuyā aṭṭhārasa, ārammaṇe nava …pe… vipāke tīṇi …pe… avigate aṭṭhārasa.
patthana19.12:7.1_0: Namicchattaniyataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca sammattaniyato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana19.12:8.1_0: Hetuyā aṭṭhārasa, ārammaṇe nava …pe… vipāke tīṇi …pe… avigate aṭṭhārasa.
patthana19.12:9.1_0: Namaggārammaṇaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca maggahetuko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
